------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.1 Help
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can get the manual for the tools by calling them with the --help command,
for example:

$ fx_bam_coverage --help

prints the help of fx_bam_coverage.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.2 Coverage computation of SAM or BAM file
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ fx_bam_coverage

